---
title: Speedy BBQ Chicken with Bacon Lardons with Wedges and Garlicky Beans
description: Ready in a mere 30 minutes, our speedy BBQ chicken lives up to its name. The highlight of this dish is the sauce, which is made with BBQ sauce and honey for a sweet and smoky flavour that’s perfect with chicken. Served with golden and crispy potato wedges and sauteed garlicky green beans, the beauty of this recipe is in the simplicity. There’s no fuss to this dish, just fresh, stand-out flavour.
